metadata.name: Windows Of Opportunity #350
metadata.description: Windows Of Opportunity displays generative stained glass like artworks in which numerous variables ensure that each mint is unique. Rare features have been implemented. 1 year of blood sweat and tears have been injected in each output. Created with p5js.

metadata.name: Generational Differences #66
metadata.description:
Based on 1-dimensional cellular automata, different pleasing patterns are produced by each generation changing the rules for the next one. Each token will produce a unique sequence of patterns, like a slideshow of mosaics. Transitions may be subtle or very drastical, since a small change on the rules has a huge effect.
Best enjoyed on fullscreen

Click anywhere on the canvas to stop/resume the creation of new generations.
Press s to download at the current resolution

Original minters will get 50% of the royalties

metadata.name: SQUARE GAMES #54
metadata.description:
Quite frankely: a lot of squares

An exploration of recursion
featuring very vibrant color combinations
Interactive

4 recursion depths
16 color palettes
4 expansion states
4 fill probabilities 
4 ghost probabilities 

Press 's' to save a high res image
Click and move mouse to explore
Press 'space' to return to original position
Press 'b' to change color of white cube
Press ‚f‘ for fullscreen
Press 'p‘ to toggle pixel perfect rendering
